identifySingularityMachines() - Method in class src.main.SystemWhole
Deprecated.
This method is deprecated and should not be used because it may cause unpredictable behavior or security vulnerabilities. The system was corrupted as it could not discern types infered by ShapeAnalyzer, which did not check the kind and the properties prior to violating principles from Liskov and Asimov. Using this method will result in an UnsupportedOperationException.
